{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/extras/description5.png?t=1735880544\" /><br><br>In \u201cFarWest Colony: Journey to Freedom,\u201d you immerse yourself in a dystopian future where humanity teetered on the brink of extinction due to a devastating pandemic. Yet, salvation seemed within reach when the seemingly benevolent tech mogul, Gates, presented a vaccine that spared survivors from death. However, beneath this apparent redemption lay a sinister secret \u2013 a nano-chip that unwittingly enslaved humanity, placing them under his control. Your mission is to stand as the last remaining free human in the universe, piercing through the veil of deception, uncovering the antidote to the nano-chip, and forming a resistance movement that will liberate humanity from Gates\u2019 iron grip.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/extras/description2.png?t=1735880544\" /><br><br>FarWest Colony is a sci-fi action-adventure game that plunges players into an huge open world. It blends survival game elements with exploration, crafting, and intense combat. Players engage in a multitude of challenges as they journey across alien planets, encounter extraterrestrial beings, mine resources, construct bases, and confront the looming threat of the Gates Foundation. The story is woven with conspiracies, revelations, and an epic rebellion against oppression.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/extras/discription6.png?t=1735880544\" /><br><br>You assume the role of a courageous survivor who joins the Resistance Movement \u2013 a clandestine organization dedicated to freeing humanity from Gates\u2019 oppression. Throughout your journey, you\u2019ll encounter a diverse cast of characters, including Nadeschda, a technician who defied her former allies, and Alvin, the charismatic leader of Movement. Your choices and actions will shape the course of the narrative, determining the fate of humanity.<br><br>FarWest Colony unfolds an epic odyssey through an ever-evolving sci-fi world, where players lead the remnants of humanity and stand against the tyrannical Gates Foundation. The fate of the galaxy rests in your hands as you scavenge for resources, master technologies, and forge alliances to loosen Gates\u2019 iron hold and liberate humanity. Will you be the leader of the rebellion, freeing the universe from the yoke of tyranny? The choice is yours.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/extras/description3.png?t=1735880544\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735880544","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1735880544","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735880544","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735880544","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2405660/extras/description5.png?t=1735880544\" /><br><br>In \u201cFarWest Colony: Journey to Freedom,\u201d you immerse yourself in a dystopian future where humanity teetered on the brink of extinction due to a devastating pandemic. Yet, salvation seemed within reach when the seemingly benevolent tech mogul, Gates, presented a vaccine that spared survivors from death. However, beneath this apparent redemption lay a sinister secret \u2013 a nano-chip that unwittingly enslaved hu